OL,5,G2000 The Hotel Inspector
OL,6,     FRuth Watson is The Hotel
OL,7,     FInspector, and she's looking to
OL,8,     Fwhip Britain's struggling
OL,9,     Fbed-and-breakfast owners and
OL,10,     Fhoteliers into shape.
OL,11,G2100 A Cruel Love: The Ruth
OL,12,     FRuth's lawyer has 24 hours to save
OL,13,     Fher life as we flash back to the
OL,14,     Fweeks leading up to David's
OL,15,     Fmurder, understanding more clearly
OL,16,     Fhow his death came about.
